{"tid":1511031,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"繼續捐612同星火基金","createTime":"2019-08-27T11:38:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T00:33:17.000Z","uid":45035,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9a34d49f09e453f305c539329aa75030a77b4f1b","tid":1511031,"uid":45035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T11:38:42.000Z","msg":"有消息指69 612等早期活動已經開始拉人<br />\n亦都為咗之後會發生嘅活動<br />\n<br />\n請繼續捐 有糧出就捐 <br />\n罷買日罷到嘅錢又捐一半<br />\n有能力捐多啲<br />\n細路仔想參與就捐一蚊留番啲錢食飯<br />\n<br />\n坊間仍有唔少人對612有懷疑態度<br />\n建議集中一post討論/直接向612查詢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3Bo1qHg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Bo1qHg.png&h=378878f7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"511ca2c8f1d21acd49bec22d743b0210eeea715d","tid":1511031,"uid":36001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T11:51:00.000Z","msg":"想問星火係唔係呢個？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sparkalliancehk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsparkalliancehk%2F&d=hq0sVSmFYzKD%2BASQGeqgxmlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=4cfc8e25\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sparkalliancehk/</a>"},{"pid":"d1423bcecc682963ccbdd2d7a2ba1fd09fcd2165","tid":1511031,"uid":287449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T12:09:35.000Z","msg":"經濟抗爭！揸現金，換美金，轉mpf，唔消費，每逢星期五同星期日都係全民宵禁日，不出街不消費！<br />\n<br />\n林鄭有張良計，我地有過牆梯－全民參與行動<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1510140\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1510140</a><br />\n<br />\n真正中共、港共春袋！金融/經濟抗爭1-page 懶人包登場！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dKNMmS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dKNMmS</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/27/181012_d18edf7a618653158ba9d392685cd8a2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08